data.description: Fabulous tri-level condo.  First level bedroom would be great as an in-law suite or guest quarters.  It's very spacious and has a full bath plus washer/dryer connections in hallway utility closet.  Second level has beautiful open kitchen,  and large family gathering area.  This level features organic bamboo flooring, granite countertops and a half bath.  Primary bedroom and bath are on the third level as well as 3rd bedroom which also has a full bath.  Additional wash-dryer hook-up are on 3rd floor.  Condo sits in centralized area to Norfolk, Virginia Beach and Chesapeake with quick access to interstate - main military bases; shopping; restaurants; and Virginia Wesleyan University.
